		<div>But consider what happens if you add the new quests in all the old zones with the movment restrictions in...suddenly there is drive as you put it to go to these zones for varying purposes, and it takes more then &amp; minute to get there. Also my original idea was focused on faction with much of your access to other zones from PoK based on a little level requirment and a FACTION with those you wanted to travel to. <br />
<br />
YES I know the PoK thing only works if you add in more content to those zones like quests, what I want to do with this thread is create of slew of ideas for the developers to do, so the devs do not have to say they will only THINK if it could be done. This when sent to them should tell them what to change with current programing options like flags/levels on the PoK stones.<br />
<br />
Before I leave this thread to be devoured by other people while im away, let me say this.  Take this thread and use it to construct a large number of easy, patchable fixes, that will help game play by adding back some of the Role playing and basic difficulty to the game.  Then when done, go and contact the devs with the ideas, and really push to make it happen. EQ must try to stay number one, and can do it with just a little effort.<br />
<br />
Tiesiaan Troiana<br />
Wizard of the 53rd rank<br />
Vacationing follower of Ro</div>
		<!-- / message -->
	
		
		
		
		
		
	
	</td>
</tr>
